&gt; 
&gt;       When it comes to the Ouija, I just want to study it to find out if it is really spirit communication, or just kinetic energy or your subconscious mind moving the planchette.
&gt; 
&gt;       I agree that we all have the ability for extra sensory perception, just some are better at it than others. Like running, for instance. We all can run, but some are naturally better at it. Still, with practice we can get better.
&gt; 
&gt;       But that is not my aim with the Ouija.
&gt; 
