&gt;          
&gt;         You forgot yawn from boredom, that&#39;s what I do.
&gt;          
&gt;         Use it, don&#39;t use it.  I don&#39;t care.  But why bother.  When people ask me I usually suggest that if they want to communicate with ... whatever why not develop the ability yourself.  - ya, I&#39;m one of those who believe anyone can.
&gt;          
&gt;         There&#39;s always the question in the back of your mind whether your partner&#39;s moving it.  The intentions of &quot;what&quot; you are talking to.  Not to mention it&#39;s too slow and limited.
&gt;          
&gt;         Besides if you take the time to develop the ability you can get more texture in the information.  Asking the board &quot;where you married?&quot; may get you a &quot;yes&quot; but a psychic might get the sense of a religious or civil ceremonhy, the garment(s) worn, other&#39;s in the party, or whether that Being approved/disapproved of their spouse (ie was it a reluctant union).
&gt;          
&gt;         ~Lori 
